title: Dumb and Dumber Improved Soundtrack High Quality
description:
The official Dumb and Dumber Soundtrack was disappointing, but an OK start. I've added songs that should have been on it but weren't, and put them in chronological order from the film. (Basically; the riff from track 6 is played more than once.)

If you're an audiophile who's watched Dumb and Dumber over 100 times, this is an ultimate collection.

All are in Apple Lossless Audio Codec, from several CDs, except the extremely rare 2 Ft O Butt Crack, which suddenly surfaced online in 2015. I included the highest quality version I could find. Boom Shack-A-Lak was from a promotional CD single distributed to radio stations.

Don't leave for a road trip without bringing this collection.

-Uncle Rick
